Albertina Francis (amụrụ na 15 Julaị 1995) bụ onye Naijiria na-egwu volleyball nke na-egwu na Ndị otu nchekwa nchekwa obodo Naijiria na ndị otu volleyball ụmụ nwanyị nke Naijiria.
Albertina na-egwu na Bọọlụ bọọlụ osimiri "b" otu maka otu egwuregwu volleyball ụmụ nwanyị nke Naịjirịa.
O meriri n'ọkwa Premiya bọọlụ bọọlụ mba otu egwuregwu na Ndị otu nchekwa nchekwa obodo Naijiria na 2019 na 2021.
Albertina so na ndị otu Naịjirịa ahọpụtara maka 2018 FIVB Asọmpi bọọlụ mba ụwa ụmụnwaanyị na Ivory Coast n'akụkụ Francisca Ikhiede na Priscilla Agera.

Ya na Tochukwu Nnourge, Francisca Ikhiede, Isabella Langu na Amarachi Uchechukwu nọchitere anya Naịjirịa na 2019 FIVB Njem ụwa nke Volleyball Snow na Bariloche, Rio Negro Argentina. Ya na ndị otu ya meriri onye ọbịa Argentina na egwuregwu mmeghe ha 2-1 (13-15, 15 Xing11).
Ndị otu Naijiria bụ ndị na-esote mgbe Kenya ruru eru maka 2020 Olimpik oge okpomọkụ.
O gosikwara na 2016 Asọmpi klọb nke Afrika na Tunisia na 2018 Asọmpi klọb nke Afrika n'Ijipt na ndị otu klọb ya.
